{
 "name": "RPlog_Triangle",
 "title": "Triangle: Three Hearts on Myrkr",
 "summary": "In the cleared yard of Talon Karrde's base on Myrkr, the Jedi Simon practices staff forms while recovering from a recent wound, watched by the smitten mechanic Orson and the red-haired Jedi Jessalyn. When Jessalyn's warm, casual affection toward Orson sparks Simon's jealousy, he withdraws coldly; Orson, sensing the tension, gently tells Jessalyn that he values her friendship more than coming between her and Simon, then retreats hurt to the barracks. Jessalyn follows to reassure him, but it is Simon she truly chases after, finally easing his jealousy and confessing that she loves him. Simon, freed at last from the possessive certainty his old teacher Cort Stasus had instilled in him, answers her confession with a passionate kiss, and the two acknowledge their love openly in the clearing.",
